{
  "id": "01-basic-usage",
  "title": "requirements-mcp-server 基本的な使い方",
  "duration": "60秒",
  "description": "MCPサーバー起動とClaude Codeでの要求追加デモ",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "duration": 5,
      "narration": "requirements-mcp-serverは、Claude Codeと連携する要求管理システムです。",
      "actions": [
        {"type": "wait", "duration": 5000}
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "start-mcp-server",
      "duration": 15,
      "narration": "まず、MCPサーバーを起動します。ターミナルでnpm run devコマンドを実行すると、21個のMCPツールが読み込まれます。",
      "actions": [
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "^{`}", "wait": 1000},
        {"type": "clipboard", "content": "cd requirements-mcp-server", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "^v", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "{ENTER}", "wait": 1000},
        {"type": "clipboard", "content": "npm run dev", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "^v", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "{ENTER}", "wait": 8000}
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "start-web-viewer",
      "duration": 12,
      "narration": "次に、Webビューアーを起動します。別のターミナルでnpm run view-serverを実行します。",
      "actions": [
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "^+{`}", "wait": 1000},
        {"type": "clipboard", "content": "npm run view-server", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "^v", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "{ENTER}", "wait": 5000},
        {"type": "wait", "duration": 5000}
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "add-requirement-claude",
      "duration": 20,
      "narration": "Claude Codeで要求を追加します。新しい要求を追加してくださいと入力すると、AIが自動的にadd requirementツールを使用します。",
      "actions": [
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "^+p", "wait": 1000},
        {"type": "clipboard", "content": "Claude", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "^v", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "{ENTER}", "wait": 2000},
        {"type": "clipboard", "content": "新しい要求を追加してください。タイトルは「ユーザー認証機能」", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "^v", "wait": 500},
        {"type": "keystroke", "keys": "{ENTER}", "wait": 12000}
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "outro",
      "duration": 8,
      "narration": "requirements-mcp-serverを使えば、AIと対話しながら効率的に要求管理ができます。",
      "actions": [
        {"type": "wait", "duration": 8000}
      ]
    }
  ]
}
